{"tid":475722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國被自家黨媒喻為世界上最民主國家 網友噓無恥","createTime":"2017-11-21T11:26:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T17:31:51.000Z","uid":43189,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b4a1830e85ea1df260d0f70d7244b3b58f548636","tid":475722,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T11:26:15.000Z","msg":"〔記者鍾麗華／綜合報導〕《求是》雜誌是中共中央委員會主辦的理論刊物，最新一期《求是》雜誌刊登北京外國語大學黨委書記、教育部中國特色社會主義理論體系研究中心特約研究員韓震的文章 ，其標題就直白地稱，「中國才是當今世界最大的民主國家」。 台灣網友噓，「臉皮超厚」、「語斃， 哄堂大笑！」、「世界上最大的笑話」、「無恥莫此為甚」。<br />\n<br />\n韓震在文章中指出，西式民主並不像西方描繪的那般光鮮，當代西式民主在很大程度上已異化為金錢政治和民粹主義政治。<br />\n<br />\n韓震表示，當代西方政治話語的實質，是試圖把以多黨制、代議制、「一人一票」等為主要特徵的資產階級民主制度確定為唯一合法的民主形式。但在西方，人民有投票權，卻沒有廣泛的參與權，只有在投票時被動員，投票後卻被丟在一邊。這樣的民主是人民形式上 有權、實際上無權的政治遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n韓震認為，「民主是人類文明的潮流。但走什麼樣的民主政治道路，沒有固定模式，不能定於一尊，更不能拿西方『標準』來評判。中國全方位迅速發展，恰好證明了當代中國正走在人類文明潮流的康莊大道之上。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2258122\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2258122&d=5HpZ%2FrAUh5jvjgaTu3OudozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=260de234\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2258122&h=89dd5928\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2258122</a>"},{"pid":"d24d889498753c7463e2fa0e59fe0672ce7fcc20","tid":475722,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T11:29:01.000Z","msg":"等睇聽朝太公同蚊匯頭版"},{"pid":"cca211b05c6fec331f1b61d10bda1f0d0a395cb3","tid":475722,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T11:36:41.000Z","msg":"自嘲"},{"pid":"d01904ecb4d1b4b26875446bca2524f031252607","tid":475722,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:16:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>五毛死曬</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/6-08-2016/ZAZQDf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F6-08-2016%2FZAZQDf.gif&h=3e028118&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7a92b86a11f446b65d936e9513fd74c8f3497a0","tid":475722,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T17:22:25.000Z","msg":"其他國家有無民主都唔輪到你生蕃支那指指點點啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a957dbd56fc41fd0b7c6d50544b30c5a144b548","tid":475722,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T17:31:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;尾有..！&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;尾有..！&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&quot;尾有..！&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&quot;通哥！！！&quot;</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}